{"tid":2359766,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴耀廷: 預見不久將來 會有不短的日子被冰冷的牆四面圍住 深信走出來的時候 春天的旭日就會到來","createTime":"2021-01-09T07:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T12:09:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fcabd69f3c558d192d04ef139ac46dc5049d0a42","tid":2359766,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/1593423760851379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBennyTaiHK%2Fposts%2F1593423760851379&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXQuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=822ed203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/1593423760851379</a><br />\n<br />\n被指違反《國安法》顛覆國家政權罪的法律學者戴耀廷，繼日前形容香港已進入寒冬，寄語港人「逆風而行」後，今日再發文指「會被冰冷的牆四面圍住」，似暗示自己或會身陷牢獄，不過他仍會專注法治的研究和寫作，深信「走出來的時候，春天的旭日就會到來。」<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷因發起民主派「35+」初選而被指違反《國安法》，日前他獲准保釋時表示，「香港進入寒冬，吹緊嘅風又猛又凍，但我相信有好多香港人會用自己嘅方法繼續逆風而行。」<br />\n<br />\n他今日再透過社交網站登出一幅由他好友創作的雪山畫像，並發文指「身心正被冷徹入骨的冰寒之氣折磨」，「幸好心頭仍有一點火未熄。也看見周圍有不少人都還是心懷希望之熖光。」他又預見自己在不久將來「會被冰冷的牆四面圍住」，不過他仍會繼續專注法治的研究和寫作，同時深信自己「走出來的時候，春天的旭日就會到來。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210109/LJ5N6MOFGZD3NHQ6G5VHKVQBYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210109%2FLJ5N6MOFGZD3NHQ6G5VHKVQBYY%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXQuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=9b801777\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210109%2FLJ5N6MOFGZD3NHQ6G5VHKVQBYY%2F&h=81fae50b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210109/LJ5N6MOFGZD3NHQ6G5VHKVQBYY/</a>"},{"pid":"234245fb13bc984af71208a227fa177b271d9e5d","tid":2359766,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"初選案放番出來嘅，走呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3f6921d5476144e595c38cbe29f2156edf1907","tid":2359766,"uid":27122,"like